1. *Grlo* me boli (My *throat* hurts)
2. Moram da popijem lek za *grlo* (I need to take medicine for my *throat*)
3. Moraš da se zagreješ, inače ćeš se prehladiti i boleti te *grlo* (You need to warm up, otherwise you'll catch a cold and your *throat* will hurt)
4. Osećam neku kvržicu u *grlu* (I feel a lump in my *throat*)
5. Pevač je imao fantastičnu izvedbu, čak je i zadnji *ton u grlu* zadržao (The singer had a fantastic performance, he even held the last *note in his throat*)
6. *Grlo* je jedan od vitalnih organa u našem telu (The *throat* is one of the vital organs in our body)
7. Ustani, moramo da idemo na posao, inače ćemo zakasniti i dobiti po *grlu* (Get up, we need to go to work, otherwise we'll be late and get it in the *throat*)
8. *Grlo* mi je suvo, treba mi malo vode (My *throat* is dry, I need some water)
9. Hladnoća me uhvatila za *grlo* (The cold caught me by the *throat*)
10. Lekar mi je rekao da imam infekciju *grla* (The doctor told me I have a *throat* infection)